### Create a new key
POST http://localhost:9000/api/v2/keys?permissions=edit_all_user_settings
Authorization: ApiSession {{api_session}}
Accept: application/json

> {% client.global.set("api_key", response.body.key); %}

### Delete a key
DELETE http://localhost:9000/api/v2/keys?key={{api_key}}
Authorization: ApiSession {{api_session}}
Accept: application/json

> {% client.global.clear("api_key"); %}

